  "title": "PROJECT ENGINEER (CONSTRUCTION)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Project execution including cost management, coordination with contractors and project related duties.</li>\n  <li>Ensure project-engineering work is completed accurately and on schedule.</li>\n  <li>To plan the works schedule and work out material requirement for purchasing department to place order.</li>\n  <li>Provides regular update of engineering status, drawings, BOMs.</li>\n  <li>To direct the daily activities of workers under his supervision. Brief the foremen and workers for every new job and monitor the progress with regular check to ensure satisfactory quality.</li>\n  <li>Regular checking of material, equipment and tools to ensure no stoppages.</li>\n  <li>Assess the skills of each worker and grade them accordingly.</li>\n  <li>Regular check on workers’ punctuality and be aware of the accommodation &amp; transport arrangement.</li>\n  <li>Always advise workers to take necessary safety precautions and work safely.</li>\n  <li>To report immediately any accidents, schedule falling behind, damage of equipment, etc.</li>\n</ul>",
